Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Maintenance workers strike
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99p6
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 May 1976
Maintenance workers strike could end New York rent control. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.